metadata.name: Garibong City People - Park Johnber
metadata.description:
He is from WASP-39b.

He was watching to colonize the Earth.
However, he was fascinated by the life of Garibong City.

So he began giving the command false information that this planet was not suitable for colonization.
The lie was soon found out.
So the command began to attack this place.

He now fights for the Garibong City.
